history.content:
Hi,

I'm a rising senior next semester, and currently I have two classes that I really want to take (CS194 and Stat156), which have a conflicting schedule, but are both only offered in fall20. Since next semester is online-based, and the final exam will not be a problem between these two courses, I wonder if the department could allow us to have a conflicting schedule? Also, who should I contact regarding this problem? Thank you!
history.subject: Allowing Schedule Conflict Next Semester?
